original_body:
@monasosh: They arrested my father & all brave human rights lawers, called them spies for hamas & iran so the ppl would turn against them #Jan25
@alaa: Amazing atmosphere at tahrir, the joy is back in the square. Massive crowd singing dancing we cannot be defeated #Jan25
@alaa: They are still shooting at us from the bridge lots injured, yet the gvt pretends it wants dialog. #Jan25
@alaa: Among martyrs of friday 28 is a 64 years old lady. #Jan25
@arabicfreedom78:
#jan25الي كل مصري حر شريف اترجاكم ان تجمعوا من تستطيعون من الوطنيين و توجهوا الي ساحة التحرير لدعم إخوانكم الثوار ضد مبارك ريتوييت
Translation!
@gheseh2000: V @SabzBrach: Maintaining a list of the dead in #Egypt. http://bit.ly/guCo1W Please let me know if you want to be part of this! #jan25
@ismaelmlt: To all egyptian people at home: Go out tomorrow and make your voice heard. I wish I could be there with you. #feb2 #egypt #jan25 #mubarak
@sarahmf732: If you don't support the protesters from the day they started til now, than you don't deserve to be called Egyptian. #jan25
@sarahbadr: NDP's net shutdown cost egypt $90 million — meanwhile, suleiman has the gall to blame econ hit on protesters. http://is.gd/H1bFGe #jan25
@mosaaberizing: Heartbreaking. A young man in tears, devastated for just knowing about the loss of his brother today morning. #Tahrir
@omar_safa: during the whole 9 days, I never heard the word "democracy" from anyone related to Mubarak's system all they talk about is stability #jan25
@jarofjuice: RT @malizomg: WTF!!?? Government van RUNS THROUGH a crowd of protesters in Egypt! #jan25 http://youtu.be/3wi3K8T3pPQ
@ANaje:
نحن الآن في انتظار رصاصة واحده تنهى كل ما يحدث

@missmayse: Update from Tahrir (cont'd, 3(3)): They could have killed my friend. If we leave them, they will kill us all. #jan25 #egypt
@_anamus: 10 million people gather at #Tahrir Square on internet! http://www.iamintahrir.com #Egypt #Jan25
====SECOND BATCH====
@ITwitius: #Egypt I can't see how we get past the weekend without either him going - OR a cataclysmic crackdown.
@ehabelbadry: 300-350k at #Tahrir square now. Everyone in very high spirits for tomorrow. Let's not let them down and march towards freedom isA. #Jan25
@Egyliberation: Calling all TRUE #Egypt citizens in #Tahrir tomorrow for the final stand against the #Mubarak corrupt regime...one word “OUT NOW“ #jan25
@Egyptcries: #Egypt #tahrir If we kick Mubarak out we get our rights forever even with the next presidents they will know for a fact Egyptians take no BS
@Hananpacha: U-Shahid back in #Egypt! via @whiteafrican New @Ushahidi Crisis Map of Egypt: http://www.u-shahid.org/cr #Jan25 #Egypt #Jan25 #Tahrir
@RawLite: #Egypt our prayers are w/you. it is always darkest before the dawn.

@angienassar: Video from today: Rock fight in #Tahrir: http://bit.ly/g06PnS #Egypt #Jan25
@fustat: R @hackneylad: Night drawing in over Cairo's Abdel Munim Riyad square and Mubarak's 'peaceful transition' continues to rage violently #Jan25
@ianinegypt: Anti-mubarak protesters are pushing back the pro mubarak protesters away from Tahrir Square. #jan25 #egypt
@sokkari: No confirmation about @ghonim release rumor. The search continues. #Egypt #jan25
@NevineZaki: A pic I took yesterday of Christians protecting Muslims during their prayers #jan25 http://yfrog.com/h02gvclj
